snippet: The physical assets of the failed Marussia Formula One team, including cars and factory equipment, have been put up for auction by administrators....

headline.print_headline: Marussia Cars and Team Equipment Put Up for Auction
headline.main: Marussia Cars and Team Equipment Put Up for Auction

lead_paragraph: The physical assets of the failed Marussia Formula One team, including cars and factory equipment, have been put up for auction by administrators.
